data">发挥一定作用</a>，但通货膨胀等经济数据肯定很重要。在本周<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/at-least-five-interesting-things-bff">的综述</a>中，我指出了<a href="https://www.briefingbook.info/p/digesting-inflation">一些证据</a>，表明即使在暂时的通货膨胀结束之后，人们也需要一段时间才能克服高通货膨胀的负面心理影响。如果价格回落到以前的水平，似乎可能会帮助人们更快地感觉好起来。</p><p>对于某些产品来说，这种情况确实会发生。自 2022 年中期以来，汽油价格已下跌三分之一以上，按美元计算低于十年前： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7ff08f9b-bf72-4d17-abec-06dd8a48788a_1318x450.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7ff08f9b-bf72-4d17-abec-06dd8a48788a_1318x450.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7ff08f9b-bf72-4d17-abec-06dd8a48788a_1318x450.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7ff08f9b-bf72-4d17-abec-06dd8a48788a_1318x450.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7ff08f9b-bf72-4d17-abec-06dd8a48788a_1318x450.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F7ff08f9b-bf72-4d17-abec-06dd8a48788a_1318x450.png" width="1318" height="450" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/7ff08f9b-bf72-4d