ze2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>美国正在赢得这场拉锯战。沙特虽然减产了，但价格还是下跌了。销量减少和每桶美元减少对沙特经济造成了毁灭性打击。该国目前正处于经济衰退之中，第三季度<a href="https://www.cnn.com/2023/11/03/economy/saudi-arabia-economy-oil-shrinks/index.html">GDP</a>年化增长率高达4.5%。</p><p>沙特人遇到了大麻烦。他们像垄断者一样左右油价的能力已经消失，因此减产只会让他们陷入贫困。这对于一个 30 年来 GDP 增长为零的国家来说是个坏消息： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48c1a3d7-3b5d-424a-8cbe-fe01fc3fffaa_1020x729.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48c1a3d7-3b5d-424a-8cbe-fe01fc3fffaa_1020x729.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48c1a3d7-3b5d-424a-8cbe-fe01fc3fffaa_1020x729.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48c1a3d7-3b5d-424a-8cbe-fe01fc3fffaa_1020x729.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48c1a3d7-3b5d-424a-8cbe-fe01fc3fffaa_1020x729.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48c1a3d7-3b5d-424a-8cbe-fe01fc3fffaa_1020x729.jpeg" width="656" height="468.84705882352944" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/48c1a3d7-3b5d-424a-8cbe-fe01fc3fffaa_1020x729.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:729,&quot;width&quot;:1020,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:656,&quot;bytes&quot;:74915,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48c1a3d7-3b5d-424a-8cbe-fe01fc3fffaa_1020x729.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48c1a3d7-3b5d-424a-8cbe-fe01fc3fffaa_1020x729.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48c1a3d7-3b5d-424a-8cbe-fe01fc3fffaa_1020x729.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F48c1a3d7-3b5d-424a-8cbe-fe01fc3fffaa_1020x729.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>那么沙特减产只是犯了一个简单的错误吗？他们认为自己仍然是摇摆乐制作人吗？或者他们限制生产还有其他原因吗？他们是否<em>能够</em>在不大幅提高开采成本的情况下维持生产？难道他们传说中的余力<a href="https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/with-world-energy-shock-saudi-oil-cushion-gets-very-thin-2022-07-08/">真的已经枯竭了吗</a>？</p><p>如果是这样，这将有助于解释该国急于<a href="https://www.forbes.com/sites/markminevich/2023/02/28/saudi-arabia-takes-a-major-leap-into-a-high-tech-future/?sh=90b0bf2b9c98">进军科技行业</a>的原因。如果沙特的石油产能比他们所表现的要弱，那么经济多元化就不仅仅是恢复增长的一种手段；有必要避免衰退。</p><h4> 2. 希望美国人对经济感到更满意吗？也许再等一年吧。</h4><p>在<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/vibes-vs-data">几天前关于“氛围”的文章</a>中，我提出，有关经济的负面叙述导致人们通过扭曲的负面视角看待大量数据。虽然我认为这是事实，但我也认为负面情绪对实体经济的改善反应缓慢。</p><p>以下是经济学家瑞安·卡明斯 (Ryan Cummings) 和尼尔·马奥尼 (Neil Mahoney) 提供的支持这一论点的一些证据： </p><div class="embedded-post-wrap" data-attrs="{&quot;id&quot;:139380815,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.briefingbook.info/p/digesting-inflation&quot;,&quot;publication_id&quot;:1002034,&quot;publication_name&quot;:&quot;Briefing Book&quot;,&quot;publication_logo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5f428911-8602-42b3-8f7b-4e63f9117721_300x300.png&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Digesting inflation&quot;,&quot;truncated_body_text&quot;:&quot;One commonly proposed explanation for weak consumer sentiment despite easing annual inflation is that consumers are still digesting the impact of prior years&#8217; price increases. While prices rose only 3.2 percent this year, they increased by a cumulative 18.6 percent over the last 3 years, and these prior price increase&#8230;&quot;,&quot;date&quot;:&quot;2023-12-04T12:15:31.967Z&quot;,&quot;like_count&quot;:1,&quot;comment_count&quot;:2,&quot;bylines&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:2717786,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Ryan Cummings&quot;,&quot;handle&quot;:&quot;ryanmgcummings&quot;,&quot;previous_name&quot;:null,&quot;photo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/60468686-71e0-4c07-b188-3314cb0ebcc2_2978x3370.jpeg&quot;,&quot;bio&quot;:&quot;Ryan Cummings is a visiting PhD student at Stanford University. He previously worked at the White House Council of Economic Advisers and at NERA Economic Consulting&quot;,&quot;profile_set_up_at&quot;:null,&quot;is_guest&quot;:true,&quot;bestseller_tier&quot;:null},{&quot;id&quot;:20026522,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Neale Mahoney&quot;,&quot;handle&quot;:&quot;nealemahoney&quot;,&quot;previous_name&quot;:null,&quot;photo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/2391223f-c156-40cb-bd9c-b3b453dd5583_1806x1762.jpeg&quot;,&quot;bio&quot;:&quot;Professor of Economics at Stanford University and George P. Shultz Fellow at SIEPR. Former White House National Economic Council. &quot;,&quot;profile_set_up_at&quot;:&quot;2023-06-02T20:38:53.248Z&quot;,&quot;is_guest&quot;:true,&quot;bestseller_tier&quot;:null}],&quot;utm_campaign&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;newsletter&quot;,&quot;language&quot;:&quot;en&quot;}" data-component-name="EmbeddedPostToDOM"><a class="embedded-post" native="true" href="https://www.briefingbook.info/p/digesting-inflation?utm_source=substack&amp;utm_campaign=post_embed&amp;utm_medium=web"><div class="embedded-post-header"><img class="embedded-post-publication-logo" src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_56,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F5f428911-8602-42b3-8f7b-4e63f9117721_300x300.png" loading="lazy"><span class="embedded-post-publication-name">简报</span></div><div class="embedded-post-title-wrapper"><div class="embedded-post-title">消化通货膨胀</div></div><div class="embedded-post-body">尽管年度通胀有所缓解，但对消费者信心疲软的一种普遍提出的解释是，消费者仍在消化前几年价格上涨的影响。虽然今年价格仅上涨 3.2%，但过去 3 年累计上涨 18.6%，而之前的价格上涨……</div><div class="embedded-post-cta-wrapper"><span class="embedded-post-cta">阅读更多</span></div><div class="embedded-post-meta">6 天前 · 1 个赞 · 2 条评论 · Ryan Cummings 和 Neale Mahoney</div></div><p>关键摘录：</p><p>虽然今年价格仅上涨 3.2%，但过去 3 年累计上涨 18.6%，之前的价格上涨可能仍对消费者信心产生负面影响。</p><blockquote><p>我们……发现[通胀对消费者信心的影响]以每年约 50% 的速度衰减……如果未来 12 个月通胀率达到 2.5%，我们估计累计下行阻力将再下降 50%。</p></blockquote><p>这是关键图： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F89b38e59-0f6c-4b2c-90f9-76cbe8a47b99_1456x819.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F89b38e59-0f6c-4b2c-90f9-76cbe8a47b99_1456x819.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F89b38e59-0f6c-4b2c-90f9-76cbe8a47b99_1456x819.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F89b38e59-0f6c-4b2c-90f9-76cbe8a47b99_1456x819.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F89b38e59-0f6c-4b2c-90f9-76cbe8a47b99_1456x819.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F89b38e59-0f6c-4b2c-90f9-76cbe8a47b99_1456x819.jpeg" width="1456" height="819" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/89b38e59-0f6c-4b2c-90f9-76cbe8a47b99_1456x819.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&qu