10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>与此同时，美国白人和亚裔美国孩子达到或接近最高点。</p><p>请注意，这<em>并不</em>意味着不同的种族群体应该在不同的“轨道”上进行评判。相反，它表明美国的教育体系有<em>能力</em>为拥有适当资源（包括家长准备）的孩子带来巨大的成果。我们大部分的改进空间来自于提升那些准备不足的孩子，所以如果我们想在这些排名中上升，这就是我们应该集中资源的地方。</p><p>不过，数学对美国来说仍然是一个大问题。美国孩子普遍<a href="https://twitter.com/cremieuxrecueil/status/1732087516734403022">在阅读</a>和<a href="https://twitter.com/cremieuxrecueil/status/1732104794372821140">科学方面</a>表现出色。但在数学方面，我们落后了： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbe5d620a-01b7-4695-810c-1992ddb4f7e6_1228x983.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbe5d620a-01b7-4695-810c-1992ddb4f7e6_1228x983.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbe5d620a-01b7-4695-810c-1992ddb4f7e6_1228x983.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbe5d620a-01b7-4695-810c-1992ddb4f7e6_1228x983.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbe5d620a-01b7-4695-810c-1992ddb4f7e6_1228x983.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbe5d620a-01b7-4695-810c-1992ddb4f