-new-data-show">PIIE</a> 。商务部的数据代表流入中国的FDI，而外管局的数据代表FDI 流入减去FDI 流出。</figcaption></figure></div><p>最近一个季度，大量资金流出中国，以至于自他们开始追踪以来，净外国直接投资<a href="https://www.reuters.com/business/wests-de-risking-starts-bite-chinas-prospects-2023-11-27/?">实际上首次出现负值</a>！ </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff7550cb3-8580-419d-bdce-3618a54ef357_680x458.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff7550cb3-8580-419d-bdce-3618a54ef357_680x458.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff7550cb3-8580-419d-bdce-3618a54ef357_680x458.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff7550cb3-8580-419d-bdce-3618a54ef357_680x458.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff7550cb3-8580-419d-bdce-3618a54ef357_680x458.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff7550cb3-8580-419d-bdce-3618a54ef357_680x458.jpeg" width="680" height="458" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/f7550cb3-8580-419d-bdce-3618a54ef357_680x458.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscre