ps://twitter.com/M_C_Klein/status/1730718997170344427">Matt C. Klein</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>现在这<em>可能</em>是因为美国人与欧洲人关心的事情不同。自 2021 年以来，我们可能已经开始真正讨厌利率，而欧洲人却没有。但一个更简单的解释是，美国人的负面情绪是由于经济指标以外的原因造成的。这个“东西”可能是一种负面的叙述——即共鸣。</p><p>举一个具体的例子，以一个名为“deusexmoniker”的用户的<a href="https://twitter.com/deusexmoniker/status/1730328615688999150">Twitter 帖子为例</a>： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ddc1a56-fb82-4ed5-b609-bf158d34b831_907x121.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ddc1a56-fb82-4ed5-b609-bf158d34b831_907x121.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ddc1a56-fb82-4ed5-b609-bf158d34b831_907x121.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ddc1a56-fb82-4ed5-b609-bf158d34b831_907x121.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ddc1a56-fb82-4ed5-b609-bf158d34b831_907x121.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8ddc1a56-fb82-4ed5-b609-bf158d34b831_907x121.jpeg" width="700" height="93.38478500551268" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/