People are realizing that the Arsenal of Democracy is goneBringing it back isn't impossible, but it will be difficult. https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/people-are-realizing-that-the-arsenal https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/people-are-realizing-that-the-arsenalNoah Smith Thu, 30 Nov 2023 09:12:17 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb2f9bc13-181e-4287-87c4-0404f6b65233_1200x865.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb2f9bc13-181e-4287-87c4-0404f6b65233_1200x865.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb2f9bc13-181e-4287-87c4-0404f6b65233_1200x865.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb2f9bc13-181e-4287-87c4-0404f6b65233_1200x865.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb2f9bc13-181e-4287-87c4-0404f6b65233_1200x865.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb2f9bc13-181e-4287-87c4-0404f6b65233_1200x865.jpeg" width="1200" height="865" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/b2f9bc13-181e-4287-87c4-0404f6b65233_1200x865.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:865,&quot;width&quot;:1200,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:259560,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb2f9bc13-181e-4287-87c4-0404f6b65233_1200x865.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb2f9bc13-181e-4287-87c4-0404f6b65233_1200x865.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb2f9bc13-181e-4287-87c4-0404f6b65233_1200x865.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb2f9bc13-181e-4287-87c4-0404f6b65233_1200x865.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：<a href="https://www.nationalmuseum.af.mil/Upcoming/Photos/igphoto/2000554840/">美国空军国家博物馆</a></figcaption></figure></div><p><em>“不要让失败主义者告诉我们已经太晚了。永远不会更早。明天会比今天晚。” ——罗斯福，1940 年 12 月</em></p><p>想象一下，你在一个看不见的魔法盾牌的保护下长大并度过了一生，该盾牌将外国征服者的军队拒之门外。盾牌在你出生之前就已经存在了，没有理由认为它<em>不会</em>存在——它只是你宇宙的背景固定装置。然后有一天，想象一下这个无形的盾牌消失了。你不会立即注意到。而耐心地潜伏在盾牌后面的征服者可能也需要一段时间才能意识到你的土地现在已经开放并且容易受到他们的军队的攻击。你会继续自己的生活一段时间，却没有意识到任何重要的事情已经发生了变化。</p><p>如果你生活在一个民主国家，我担心这几乎描述了你现在所处的情况。</p><p>这些天我对<a href="https://ourworldindata.org/grapher/countries-democracies-autocracies-row">这张图表</a>思考了很多： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F32df0702-c6a0-4705-a982-f0a2209d209e_1020x844.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F32df0702-c6a0-4705-a982-f0a2209d209e_1020x844.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F32df0702-c6a0-4705-a982-f0a2209d209e_1020x844.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F32df0702-c6a0-4705-a982-f0a2209d209e_1020x844.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F32df0702-c6a0-4705-a982-f0a2209d209e_1020x844.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F32df0702-c6a0-4705-a982-f0a2209d209e_1020x844.jpeg" width="1020" height="844" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/32df0702-c6a0-4705-a982-f0a2209d209e_1020x844.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:844,&quot;width&quot;:1020,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:155587,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F32df0702-c6a0-4705-a982-f0a2209d209e_1020x844.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F32df0702-c6a0-4705-a982-f0a2209d209e_1020x844.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F32df0702-c6a0-4705-a982-f0a2209d209e_1020x844.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F32df0702-c6a0-4705-a982-f0a2209d209e_1020x844.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>为什么民主从 1944 年的边缘政府形式发展到 2010 年统治半个世界的体系？是因为民主在经济上更有利吗？是因为人们变得更富有而要求更多的民主吗？或许。但这也许是美国实力的幸运结果。美国的<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Military_production_during_World_War_II#United_States_World_War_II_GDP_(compared_to_other_countries)">军工生产</a>在第二次世界大战中粉碎了法西斯帝国（包括<a href="https://www.rferl.org/a/did-us-lend-lease-aid-tip-the-balance-in-soviet-fight-against-nazi-germany/30599486.html">拯救了苏联</a>），在冷战期间捍卫了“自由世界”，并在之后遏制了“流氓国家”。</p><p>富兰克林·罗斯福是对的——美国确实是民主的军火库。维基百科上的一张二战生产数据的小表准确地显示了战争是如何获胜的： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff2106037-ccee-43fd-80ea-776b8307e9b7_550x288.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff2106037-ccee-43fd-80ea-776b8307e9b7_550x288.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff2106037-ccee-43fd-80ea-776b8307e9b7_550x288.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff2106037-ccee-43fd-80ea-776b8307e9b7_550x288.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff2106037-ccee-43fd-80ea-776b8307e9b7_550x288.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff2106037-ccee-43fd-80ea-776b8307e9b7_550x288.jpeg" width="484" height="253.44" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/f2106037-ccee-43fd-80ea-776b8307e9b7_550x288.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:288,&quot;width&quot;:550,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:484,&quot;bytes&quot;:47930,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff2106037-ccee-43fd-80ea-776b8307e9b7_550x288.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff2106037-ccee-43fd-80ea-776b8307e9b7_550x288.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff2106037-ccee-43fd-80ea-776b8307e9b7_550x288.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff2106037-ccee-43fd-80ea-776b8307e9b7_550x288.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Military_production_during_World_War_II#Production_summaries_1939%E2%80%931945">维基百科</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>美国是迄今为止最大的生产国，建造的大型船舶数量是所有其他参战国总和的两倍，<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/World_War_II_aircraft_production">飞机</a>数量至少是其他参战国的两倍。该国强大的汽车、飞机和船舶工业花了一段时间才提高了战争生产，但当他们这样做时，地球上没有任何东西可以与之匹敌。 <em><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Freedoms-Forge-American-Business-Produced/dp/0812982045">《自由的熔炉》</a></em>和 <em><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Destructive-Creation-American-Business-Politics/dp/0812248333">《破坏性创造》</a></em>等书籍将告诉您如何实现这一目标的故事。这种工业主导地位延续到了冷战时期，德国和日本这两个主要制造业国家成为美国的盟友，这进一步巩固了这种地位。苏联可以用核武库威胁西方，但在战争生产方面，自由世界的产量可能超过共产主义世界。</p><p>自世界大战前以来，这种情况第一次发生了变化。中国作为制造业强国的崛起，与<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-war-economy-sizing-up-the-new">美国和整个欧洲的总和相抗衡</a>，总是会带来重大挑战。但自世纪之交以来，美国国防工业基础的彻底萎缩使得这场竞争不再那么激烈。军事生产潜力的天平现在牢牢地站在专制国家一边。</p><p>这听起来像是一个令人震惊的说法。但<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/were-not-ready-for-the-big-one">我最近发布的有关与中国的战争威胁的帖子</a>中的三张图片非常清楚地说明了这一点： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8030881d-e3bf-444a-877e-9456ee439477_902x497.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8030881d-e3bf-444a-877e-9456ee439477_902x497.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8030881d-e3bf-444a-877e-9456ee439477_902x497.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8030881d-e3bf-444a-877e-9456ee439477_902x497.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8030881d-e3bf-444a-877e-9456ee439477_902x497.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,