e:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1cb8ad2a-7ddf-4b3f-b492-a551fbdc5904_918x477.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1cb8ad2a-7ddf-4b3f-b492-a551fbdc5904_918x477.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>如果美国尽最大努力也只能生产出1995年炮弹的1/9，而中国可以生产相当于美国200倍的舰艇，那么二战和冷战时期存在的民主军械库就消失了。即使这些数字被夸大了三倍，也仍然意味着民主军械库已经消失。</p><p>我并不是荒野中唯一一个为此大喊大叫的人。评论界的很多人也有同样的认识。 <a href="https://foreignpolicy.com/2023/11/16/us-russia-china-gaza-ukraine-world-war-defense-security-strategy/">A. 韦斯·米切尔 (A. Wess Mitchell) 在《外交政策》中</a>说道：</p><blockquote><p>美国距离一场可能输掉的<a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/america-needs-to-be-ready-for-war-taiwan-ukraine-gaza-b57f6a84?mod=opinion_lead_pos9">世界大战</a>只有一步之遥。世界上三个最具战略意义的地区中的两个地区存在着需要美国关注的严重冲突……</p><p>美国以前曾打过多线战争。但在过去的冲突中，它总是能够战胜对手。但现在情况已不再如此：中国海军的舰艇数量已经超过美国，而且其<a href="https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/defence/china-vs-the-world-heres-a-look-at-naval-power-in-the-pacific-in-numbers/articleshow/86285514.cms">增长</a>量相当于整个法国海军（据法国海军参谋长称，大约有 130 艘舰艇）。四年。相比之下，美国海军<a href="https://news.usni.org/2022/07/26/navys-force-design-2045-plans-for-373-ship-fleet-150-unmanned-vessels">计划</a>在未来十年内增加 75 艘舰艇……</p><p>除非美国的国防工业基地井然有序，否则[保卫美国盟友]是不可能的。自俄罗斯-乌克兰战争爆发以来，美国国防生产总量<a href="https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/IPB52300S">仅增加了 10%</a> ，尽管这场战争表明重大冲突中军用弹药的消耗量高得惊人。</p></blockquote><p>以下是<a href="https://www.aei.org/op-eds/the-u-s-navy-is-falling-behind-china-and-the-pentagon-knows-it/">美国企业研究所的 Mackenzie Eaglen 的</a>报道：</p><blockquote><p>五角大楼最近发布了关于中国军事发展的<a href="https://media.defense.gov/2023/Oct/19/2003323409/-1/-1/1/2023-MILITARY-AND-SECURITY-DEVELOPMENTS-INVOLVING-THE-PEOPLES-REPUBLIC-OF-CHINA.PDF">年度报告</a>，其调查结果很明确……我们的军队正在努力跟上……</p><p>中国在<a href="https://media.defense.gov/2023/Oct/19/2003323409/-1/-1/1/2023-MILITARY-AND-SECURITY-DEVELOPMENTS-INVOLVING-THE-PEOPLES-REPUBLIC-OF-CHINA.PDF#page=185">造船</a>能力和造船厂能力方面不断超越美国……虽然中国海军预计将在短短五年内增长近20%，但海军<a href="https://www.govexec.com/media/navy_2024_shipbuilding_plan.pdf#page=24">24财年造船计划</a>预计其规模将继续缩小。到 2025 年，我们的船队将缩减至 285 艘，但到 2030 年仍将低于目前的规模，即 290 艘，因为船舶退役速度持续超过新船建造速度……</p><p>预计到 2030 年，美国潜艇舰队将只剩下 57 艘……最近潜艇<a href="https://crsreports.congress.gov/product/pdf/RL/RL32418/260#page=10">基地维护积压</a>已导致近 40% 的美国潜艇舰队无法使用……年复一年，美国海军仍然背负着预算不断<a href="https://www.realcleardefense.com/articles/2023/07/08/buying_power_is_the_invisible_shortfall_of_the_2024_defense_budget_request_964806.html">缩减</a>且不 <a href="https://www.19fortyfive.com/2023/10/chaos-in-congress-must-not-damage-americas-military/">确定性</a>越来越大。</p></blockquote><p> <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/02/27/opinion/a-war-with-china-would-reach-deep-into-american-society.html">类似</a><a href="https://warontherocks.com/2023/08/you-go-to-war-with-the-industrial-base-you-have-not-the-industrial-base-you-want/">效果</a>的其他<a href="https://www.businessinsider.com/us-looks-overseas-for-warship-repairs-amid-shipyard-delays-2023-10?amp">文章</a>也在<a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/americas-industrial-base-isnt-ready-for-war-with-china-weapons-defense-funding-military-war-conflict-taiwan-supplier-11660833718">其他地方</a> <a href="https://features.csis.org/preparing-the-US-industrial-base-to-deter-conflict-with-China/">出现</a>，但<a href="https://twitter.com/kiteandkeymedia/status/1724781801510699039">您已经明白了要点</a>。</p><p>顺便说一句，重要的是要澄清，“民主军火库”一词并不是指<em>我们现有军队的规模</em>，也不是指我们的<em>军费开支</em>。它指的是我们的<em>军事生产潜力</em>——在与中国这样的大国进行长期常规战争的情况下，我们<em>可以制造</em>多少军事装备。尽管哀叹国防工业基础萎缩的人们大谈军事预算的缩减，但更深层次的问题是美国的去工业化。在过去的二十年里，美国经济中用于生产实体产品的部分越来越少，而中国经济的工业化程度仍然高于美国的任何主要盟友： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdf121f8f-dcad-4f6d-83f1-11d60a251ef1_1020x720.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdf121f8f-dcad-4f6d-83f1-11d60a251ef1_1020x720.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdf121f8f-dcad-4f6d-83f1-11d60a251ef1_1020x720.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdf121f8f-dcad-4f6d-83f1-11d60a251ef1_1020x720.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdf121f8f-dcad-4f6d-83f1-11d60a251ef1_1020x720.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdf121f8f-dcad-4f6d-83f1-11d60a251ef1_1020x720.jpeg" width="694" height="489.88235294117646" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/df121f8f-dcad-4f6d-83f1-11d60a251ef1_1020x720.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:720,&quot;width&quot;:1020,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:694,&quot;bytes&quot;:119788,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdf121f8f-dcad-4f6d-83f1-11d60a251ef1_1020x720.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdf121f8f-dcad-4f6d-83f1-11d60a251ef1_1020x720.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdf121f8f-dcad-4f6d-83f1-11d60a251ef1_1020x720.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fdf121f8f-dcad-4f6d-83f1-11d60a251ef1_1020x720.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>制造并不是一支强大军队所需要的唯一东西——软件、物流和其他东西也有帮助。但用于战争的大部分经济产出都是有形武器和物资。多年来，美国专家一直忽视制造业的重要性，认为医疗保健和教育等服务业是未来好工作的更重要来源。不管这是否属实，它完全忽视了制造业的军事重要性。这种对去工业化的漠不关心的态度现在再次困扰着我们。</p><p>不管怎样，我会谈谈我们如何能够恢复民主军械库，但首先，我认为首先解释一下为什么它很重要。显然，如果你在波兰或韩国，美国的力量和保护对你来说非常重要。但许多美国人自然地觉得他们受到两边海洋的保护，并且可以放心地忽视乌克兰和台湾等国家发生的事情。这是灾难性的自满。如果你不担心民主军械库的消失，你应该担心。</p><h4>缺乏民主军械库对你的未来意味着什么</h4><p><a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/people-are-realizing-that-the-arsenal">阅读更多</a></p>; 
The U.S. must not ignore IndonesiaWe have the opportunity to befriend an Asian country with a huge population, a large and growing economy, and a strategic location. https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-us-must-not-ignore-indonesia https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-us-must-not-ignore-indonesiaNoah Smith Wed, 29 Nov 2023 10:08:53 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1124f5ba-7301-47ea-97c7-a04a0fb6f869_1024x682.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1124f5ba-7301-47ea-97c7-a04a0fb6f869_1024x682.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1124f5ba-7301-47ea-97c7-a04a0fb6f869_1024x682.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1124f5ba-7301-47ea-97c7-a04a0fb6f869_1024x682.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1124f5ba-7301-47ea-97c7-a04a0fb6f869_1024x682.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1124f5ba-7301-47ea-97c7-a04a0fb6f869_1024x682.jpeg" width="1024" height="682" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/1124f5ba-7301-47ea-97c7-a04a0fb6f869_1024x682.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:682,&quot;width&quot;:1024,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:151688,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1124f5ba-7301-47ea-97c7-a04a0fb6f869_1024x682.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1124f5ba-7301-47ea-97c7-a04a0fb6f869_1024x682.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1124f5ba-7301-47ea-97c7-a04a0fb6f869_1024x682.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F1124f5ba-7301-47ea-97c7-a04a0fb6f869_1024x682.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://id.usembassy.gov/president-joseph-r-biden-and-president-joko-widodo-announce-the-u-s-indonesia-comprehensive-strategic-partnership/">国务院</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>随着中国在亚洲实力的增强，其他国家一直在组建<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/at-least-five-interesting-things-462">防御联盟</a>以制衡它。最近的例子包括日本与越南新的<a href="https://apnews.com/article/japan-vietnam-china-security-partnership-98d1f48de053faf9ba7e71f21187bfb6">军事和经济合作</a>、日本<a href="https://www.economist.com/asia/2023/11/09/chinas-aggression-brings-japan-and-the-philippines-closer">与菲律宾更密切的合作</a>、 <a href="https://www.usnews.com/news/world/articles/2023-11-27/vietnam-upgrades-ties-with-japan-to-highest-level">越南与印度的</a>关系升级等等。其中许多国家都将美国视为保护来源，这就是为什么越南最近<a href="https://www.cfr.org/blog/assessing-bolstered-us-vietnam-relationship">升级了与华盛顿的关系</a>，为什么印度总理今年早些时候<a href="https://www.usip.org/publications/2023/06/modis-trip-washington-marks-new-heights-us-india-ties">加深了与美国的军事合作</a>，以及为什么菲律宾允许美国建设其领土上<a href="https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-reveals-locations-4-new-strategic-sites-us-military-pact-2023-04-03/">有四个新的军事基地</a>。</p><p>但其中一项合作伙伴关系似乎<a href="https://twitter.com/Blake_Allen13/status/1724254643587305491">并未受到关注</a>，很少受到新闻报道和关注。本月早些时候，就在旧金山亚太经合组织峰会之前，美国和印度尼西亚<a href="https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefing-room/statements-releases/2023/11/13/fact-sheet-president-joseph-r-biden-and-president-joko-widodo-announce-the-u-s-indonesia-comprehensive-strategic-partnership/">宣布建立全面战略伙伴关系</a>。这需要采取各种举措——经济投资、气候、健康和恐怖主义等问题上的合作等。它还包括军事合作。尽管中国从未被提及，但中国的存在在该协议中显然显得尤为突出，其中谈到了应对来自“国家和非国家行为者”的网络安全威胁、提高印度尼西亚的“海域意识”等等。</p><p>这项协议是在多年来<a href="https://thediplomat.com/2023/09/us-indonesia-security-relations-flourish-in-a-changing-indo-pacific/">不断加强的军事关系</a>和<a href="https://www.thejakartapost.com/indonesia/2023/08/31/indonesian-us-troops-begin-super-garuda-shield-joint-drills.html">联合演习</a>之后达成的。印度尼西亚担忧的根源在于中国声称几乎整个南海都是其领土。中国的主权声索包括印度尼西亚纳土纳群岛附近的<a href="https://www.globaldefensecorp.com/2020/06/20/indonesian-natuna-island-could-be-pla-navys-choke-point/">海域</a>。 2021年， <a href="https://thediplomat.com/2021/12/china-demanded-halt-to-indonesian-drilling-near-natuna-islands-report/">中国要求</a>印尼停止在这些海域钻探石油和天然气；印尼<a href="https://www.reuters.com/article/us-indonesia-china-southchinasea/indonesia-rejects-chinas-claims-over-south-china-sea-idUSKBN1Z01RE/">拒绝了中国的主张</a>，两国在该地区长期对峙。印度尼西亚领导人知道，如果没有美国的援助，他们将很容易遭受更多此类欺凌。</p><p>但这并不意味着印度尼西亚已准备好成为美国最好的朋友。民意调查几乎都显示，尽管印尼人喜欢美国，但他们对中国也同样持积极态度，并希望在两国之间保持中立立场。这是一个例子： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F142b8760-aa86-444c-bf43-b96762088448_1087x1200.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F142b8760-aa86-444c-bf43-b96762088448_1087x1200.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F142b8760-aa86-444c-bf43-b96762088448_1087x1200.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F142b8760-aa86-444c-bf43-b96762088448_1087x1200.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F142b8760-aa86-444c-bf43-b96762088448_1087x1200.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F142b8760-aa86-444c-bf43-b96762088448_1087x1200.jpeg" width="622" height="686.6605335786569" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/142b8760-aa86-444c-bf43-b96762088448_1087x1200.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1200,&quot;width&quot;:1087,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:622,&quot;bytes&quot;:112419,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F142b8760-aa86-444c-bf43-b96762088448_1087x1200.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F142b8760-aa86-444c-bf43-b96762088448_1087x1200.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F142b8760-aa86-444c-bf43-b96762088448_1087x1200.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F142b8760-aa86-444c-bf43-b96762088448_1087x1200.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">来源： <a href="https://ecfr.eu/publication/living-in-an-a-la-carte-world-what-european-policymakers-should-learn-from-global-public-opinion/">ECFR</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>皮尤中心还有<a href="https://www.pewresearch.org/global/2023/11/06/comparing-views-of-the-us-and-china-in-24-countries/">更多民意调查问题</a>，但都显示出同样的情况。与此同时， <a href="https://csis-website-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/s3fs-public/2023-08/230807_Poling_Influence_SoutheastAsia.pdf?VersionId=eJgGM04iKBt0YI9fWu.co9bdSNj44rFc">战略与国际研究中心（CSIS）研究了多项调查</a>后发现，尽管印尼人对美国的态度比对中国的态度稍好一些，但该国的精英却持中立态度。</p><p>换句话说，在亚洲正在形成的巨大竞争中，印度尼西亚基本上是一个“摇摆国家”。鉴于其庞大的人口、战略位置以及庞大且不断增长的经济，它可能是最重要的摇摆州。但总的来说，美国人似乎几乎完全没有意识到这一点——事实上，他们根本不知道印度尼西亚的存在。</p><h4>印度尼西亚：幅员辽阔、重要但仍不为人所知</h4><p>关于印度尼西亚，首先要认识到的是，它真的非常非常大。它是世界第四人口大国，人口数量约为美国的 84%，并且是东南亚最大的国家： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F26ac3ecb-3329-42b9-a806-19e34a5f1d4c_1020x720.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F26ac3ecb-3329-42b9-a806-19e34a5f1d4c_1020x720.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F26ac3ecb-3329-42b9-a806-19e34a5f1d4c_1020x720.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F26ac3ecb-3329-42b9-a806-19e34a5f1d4c_1020x720.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F26ac3ecb-3329-42b9-a806-19e34a5f1d4c_1020x720.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F26ac3ecb-3329-42b9-a806-19e34a5f1d4c_1020x720.jpeg" width="1020" height="720" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/26ac3ecb-3329-42b9-a806-19e34a5f1d4c_1020x720.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:720,&quot;width&quot;:1020,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:86184,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F26ac3ecb-3329-42b9-a806-19e34a5f1d4c_1020x720.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F26ac3ecb-3329-42b9-a806-19e34a5f1d4c_1020x720.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F26ac3ecb-3329-42b9-a806-19e34a5f1d4c_1020x720.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F26ac3ecb-3329-42b9-a806-19e34a5f1d4c_1020x720.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>稳定且相当快速的经济增长正在将人口数量转化为经济影响力。印度尼西亚比东南亚和南亚的大多数其他国家更富裕，但其增长速度与大多数国家保持同步： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4122dc68-2aee-4751-b3a1-23285d509153_1020x735.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4122dc68-2aee-4751-b3a1-23285d509153_1020x735.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4122dc68-2aee-4751-b3a1-23285d509153_1020x735.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4122dc68-2aee-4751-b3a1-23285d509153_1020x735.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4122dc68-2aee-4751-b3a1-23285d509153_1020x735.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4122dc68-2aee-4751-b3a1-23285d509153_1020x735.jpeg" width="1020" height="735" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/4122dc68-2aee-4751-b3a1-23285d509153_1020x735.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:735,&quot;width&quot;:1020,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:133930,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4122dc68-2aee-4751-b3a1-23285d509153_1020x735.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4122dc68-2aee-4751-b3a1-23285d509153_1020x735.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4122dc68-2aee-4751-b3a1-23285d509153_1020x735.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4122dc68-2aee-4751-b3a1-23285d509153_1020x735.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>印度尼西亚究竟是如何实现这一增长的，是一个非常有趣的故事。它是世界上为数不多的从制造业强国转向自然资源出口国且没有放缓步伐的国家之一，目前正<a href="https://setkab.go.id/en/president-jokowi-pushes-for-development-of-integrated-industrial-ecosystem/">试图回归</a>。我去年写过一篇关于它的文章： </p><div class="digest-post-embed" data-attrs="{&quot;nodeId&quot;:&quot;5030c9f5-42a9-4f40-8960-c217d994d0e5&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;I&#8217;ve been writing a series of posts about economic development. The last 20 years have seen a marked acceleration in the rate at which poorer countries &#8212; not just China, but many countries &#8212; are catching up to richer ones. Among the success stories I&#8217;ve profiled so far are&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;sm&quot;,&quot;isEditorNode&quot;:true,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Indonesia: The most amazing development story on Earth?&quot;,&quot;publishedBylines&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:8243895,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Noah Smith&quot;,&quot;bio&quot;:&quot;Econ blogger&quot;,&quot;photo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/89fd964a-586f-461a-9f5a-ea4587d45728_397x441.png&quot;,&quot;is_guest&quot;:false,&quot;bestseller_tier&quot;:10000}],&quot;post_date&quot;:&quot;2022-06-28T19:25:52.624Z&quot;,&quot;cover_image&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fba33f3a0-5d84-438d-93c3-9690159063db_687x1023.jpeg&quot;,&quot;cover_image_alt&quot;:null,&quot;canonical_url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/indonesia-the-most-amazing-development&quot;,&quot;section_name&quot;:null,&quot;id&quot;:61144766,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;newsletter&quot;,&quot;reaction_count&quot;:173,&quot;comment_count&quot;:41,&quot;publication_name&quot;:&quot;Noahpinion&quot;,&quot;publication_logo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F04281755-2cd6-42e5-a496-e69153abebb2_281x281.png&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true}"></div><p>除了成为美国商品的重要潜在市场之外，印度尼西亚<a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2023-11-02/supply-chain-latest-mexico-morocco-poland-vietnam-win-in-supply-shift?sref=R8NfLgwS">还可能成为美国供应链“友好外包”的关键地点</a>。最近的美国与印度尼西亚协议<a href="https://www.state.gov/new-partnership-with-indonesia-to-explore-semiconductor-supply-chain-opportunities/">包括有关半导体行业的关键内容</a>：</p><blockquote><p>美国国务院将与印度尼西亚政府合作，根据 2022 年 CHIPS 法案创建的国际技术安全与创新 (ITSI) 基金，探索全球半导体生态系统发展和多样化的机会……美国将印度尼西亚视为合作伙伴确保半导体供应链能够跟上正在进行的数字化转型……此次合作凸显了在印度尼西亚扩展该行业的巨大潜力，从而使美国和印度尼西亚都受益。</p><p>该合作伙伴关系首先将审查印度尼西亚当前的半导体生态系统、监管框架以及劳动力和基础设施需求。此次审查的结果将为未来开发这一关键部门的潜在合作提供信息。</p></blockquote><p>换句话说，美国政府正准备就如何使印尼成为更适合制造业外国直接投资的目的地向印尼提供建议。如果这一努力取得成功，印度尼西亚作为投资目的地的吸引力可能会远远超出芯片行业。凭借其丰富的矿藏，它可能有助于<a href="https://www.economist.com/briefing/2022/11/14/indonesia-is-poised-for-a-boom-politics-permitting">打破中国对关键矿物加工和电池制造的束缚</a>。</p><p>但印度尼西亚对美国的战略重要性超出了其经济潜力。它位于印度洋和太平洋之间的重要贸易路线沿线——<a href="https://chinapower.csis.org/much-trade-transits-south-china-sea/">中国约 40% 的货物贸易</a>经过南海。这项贸易必须经过印度尼西亚三个海峡之一——马六甲海峡、巽他海峡和龙目岛——否则就要绕过澳大利亚。如果中美之间确实爆发重大冲突，印度尼西亚周围的水域和岛屿可能会成为大部分战斗的地点，就像第二次世界大战中那样。</p><p>最重要的是，印度尼西亚的成功将促进美国希望在该地区鼓励的价值观。它与菲律宾一样，是东南亚<a href="https://freedomhouse.org/countries/freedom-world/scores">最自由、最民主的国家</a>，在经历了数十年的军事独裁后成功过渡到民主。作为世界上最大的穆斯林国家，印度尼西亚提倡<a href="https://theconversation.com/how-the-worlds-biggest-islamic-organization-drives-religious-reform-in-indonesia-and-seeks-to-influence-the-muslim-world-165064">宽容的伊斯兰教</a>，值得提升。</p><p>换句话说，美国有充分的理由将印度尼西亚视为一个非常重要的国家，可以对其进行促进、援助和合作。然而，尽管最近达成了协议，美国总体上对印度尼西亚的关注相对较少。一位印度尼西亚商人曾称他的国家是世界上“最大的隐形物体”。</p><p>如果美国想要改变这种状况并利用印度尼西亚提供的所有潜力，就需要更加努力地思考它能为印度尼西亚做些什么。</p><h4>美国需要为印度尼西亚做些什么</h4><p><a href="https://csis-website-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/s3fs-public/2023-08/230807_Poling_Influence_SoutheastAsia.pdf?VersionId=eJgGM04iKBt0YI9fWu.co9bdSNj44rFc">CSIS的报告</a>发现，印尼人倾向于将美国主要视为<em>军事大国</em>和军事伙伴，而将中国视为更重要的<em>经济</em>大国和伙伴。因此，为了深化美印尼伙伴关系，美国需要重点加强其薄弱领域——经济。</p><p>更深层次的美国和印度尼西亚经济伙伴关系必须从基础设施开始。印尼总统佐科·维多多已将基础设施建设作为其经济政策的<a href="https://www.pwc.com/id/en/media-centre/infrastructure-news/september-2022/jokowi-builds-1700-km-toll-roads-2-1-times-the-length-of-the-previous-era.html">重要组成部分</a>。该基础设施必须通过<a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/view/articles/2019-05-20/indonesia-s-infrastructure-debt-binge-follows-china-model?sref=R8NfLgwS">借贷</a>来资助。大部分资金是在国内借来的，但印度尼西亚也在寻求外国融资。</p><p>一般来说，外国基础设施融资不仅仅涉及贷款，通常还涉及“优惠融资”（以低于市场利率的贷款，这实际上是部分赠款）和技术援助。美国基本上没有这样做。日本作为美国的重要盟友，无疑已经挺身而出，帮助印度尼西亚在雅加达<a href="https://www.railjournal.com/passenger/metros/japanese-indonesian-jv-wins-jakarta-mrt-metro-contract/">建设地铁系统</a>，并<a href="https://www.japantimes.co.jp/news/2022/11/15/national/kishida-indonesia-yen-loans/">承诺为道路建设提供资金</a>。</p><p>但印尼真正转向的国家是中国。在“一带一路”倡议下，中国向印尼<a href="https://www.lemonde.fr/en/international/article/2023/11/05/full-steam-ahead-for-china-s-belt-and-road-initiative-in-indonesia_6230012_4.html">提供了数十亿</a>美元的基础设施贷款，并承诺提供<a href="https://www.pbs.org/newshour/world/indonesia-says-china-has-pledged-21-billion-in-new-investment-to-strengthen-ties">数百亿美元</a>的贷款——比日本多一个数量级。最重要、最令人印象深刻的中国融资项目是印度尼西亚第一条连接雅加达和万隆的高速铁路： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3541fbd-15e9-45a4-a2fc-d8b5c6e9dc0c_1146x644.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3541fbd-15e9-45a4-a2fc-d8b5c6e9dc0c_1146x644.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3541fbd-15e9-45a4-a2fc-d8b5c6e9dc0c_1146x644.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3541fbd-15e9-45a4-a2fc-d8b5c6e9dc0c_1146x644.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3541fbd-15e9-45a4-a2fc-d8b5c6e9dc0c_1146x644.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3541fbd-15e9-45a4-a2fc-d8b5c6e9dc0c_1146x644.jpeg" width="1146" height="644" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/e3541fbd-15e9-45a4-a2fc-d8b5c6e9dc0c_1146x644.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:644,&quot;width&quot;:1146,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:330723,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3541fbd-15e9-45a4-a2fc-d8b5c6e9dc0c_1146x644.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3541fbd-15e9-45a4-a2fc-d8b5c6e9dc0c_1146x644.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3541fbd-15e9-45a4-a2fc-d8b5c6e9dc0c_1146x644.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fe3541fbd-15e9-45a4-a2fc-d8b5c6e9dc0c_1146x644.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">作者： <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/w/index.php?curid=140655050">Naufal Farras</a> ，CC BY-SA 4.0</figcaption></figure></div><p>美国为印度尼西亚创造了哪些类似的奇迹？什么都没有。维多多在2017年赞扬中国的基础设施融资时，强烈暗示了与美国的对比：</p><blockquote><p>这不仅仅是说说而已，而是要实际建造一些东西。从机场到铁路，这些都是我们看得见、摸得着的行业。</p></blockquote><p>这项基础设施建设工作有助于巩固两国之间更广泛的经济联系；中国已取代日本和东南亚其他国家，成为印度尼西亚的<a href="https://oec.world/en/profile/country/idn">主要贸易伙伴</a>。鉴于这一切，难怪印尼人认为中国是比美国更重要的经济大国！</p><p>但中国在印尼的经济影响力远非无懈可击。总体而言，“一带一路”项目<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/how-chinas-debt-traps-actually-work">大多是失败的</a>，为不经济的项目提供资金，这些项目充满了腐败、成本超支和延误，并让借款国承担了由此产生的坏账。这在印度尼西亚也是<a href="https://jamestown.org/program/ten-years-on-how-is-the-belt-and-road-initiative-faring-in-indonesia/">如此</a>：</p><blockquote><p>印度尼西亚共价值 52 亿美元的“一带一路”项目中有 9 个涉及丑闻、争议或涉嫌违规行为——位居世界第二，仅次于巴基斯坦……印度尼西亚欠中国债权人的债务持续攀升，2022 年 3 月达到 220.1 亿美元。</p></blockquote><p>印度尼西亚的表现比其他一些“一带一路”借款国要好一些，因为它<a href="https://www.lowyinstitute.org/publications/concerns-over-china-backed-high-speed-railway-do-not-derail-indonesia-s-agency">以更精明的方式</a>与中国打交道，拒绝将其政府预算作为从中国借款的抵押品。因此，成本超支等问题与其说是陷阱，不如说是烦恼。</p><p>但印度尼西亚可能更喜欢一个不要求其在谈判中采取如此强硬态度、并且不太容易做粗制滥造的基础设施合作伙伴。 <a href="https://warontherocks.com/2019/04/quality-infrastructure-japans-robust-challenge-to-chinas-belt-and-road/">日本就是这样的合作伙伴</a>，因为它的基础设施质量最高，但它没有资金与中国相媲美。我们需要的是一个美日联合项目来为印度尼西亚的基础设施融资，其中美国提供大部分现金，日本提供技术援助。这方面的一些努力<a href="https://asia.nikkei.com/Politics/International-relations/Indo-Pacific/US-and-Japan-plan-Belt-and-Road-alternative-for-Indo-Pacific">已经在进行</a>，但需要针对印度尼西亚，而美国需要投入更多现金。</p><p>美国需要做的第二件事是成为印尼商品的更大市场。包括印度尼西亚在内的跨太平洋伙伴关系协定本可以实现这一目标，但美国不幸地取消了 TPP。相反，美国现在可能需要的是更有针对性的贸易举措——鼓励印度尼西亚向美国提供加工金属、电池和低端半导体等美国目前依赖中国提供的商品的措施。</p><p>美国可以向印度尼西亚提供的第三件事是制造业外国直接投资。维多多致力于让印度尼西亚从资源出口转向工业，扭转自 1997 年亚洲金融危机以来出现的部分去工业化趋势​​。美国可以通过帮助那些希望实现多元化的企业从中国转向印度尼西亚来实现这一目标。</p><p>如果美国做到这些，印尼将成为一个更亲密、更可靠的伙伴。地缘政治利益将是巨大的，经济利益也将是实实在在的。印度尼西亚可能是亚洲的最后一块拼图——但在此之前，美国首先必须表明它愿意提供具体和切实的利益。当然，最糟糕的事情是美国继续忽视这个巨大的、不断增长的、具有重要战略意义的国家。 </p><div><hr></div><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?"><span>现在订阅</span></a></p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-us-must-not-ignore-indonesia?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"> <a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-us-must-not-ignore-indonesia?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share"><span>分享</span></a></p><div id="youtube2-E4qo_PkR7WE" class="youtube-wrap" data-attrs="{&quot;videoId&quot;:&quot;E4qo_PkR7WE&quot;,&quot;startTime&quot;:null,&quot;endTime&quot;:null}" data-component-name="Youtube2ToDOM"><div class="youtube-inner"><iframe src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/E4qo_PkR7WE?rel=0&amp;autoplay=0&amp;showinfo=0&amp;enablejsapi=0" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" gesture="media" allow="autoplay; fullscreen" allowautoplay="true" allowfullscreen="true" width="728" height="409"></iframe></div></div> ; 
Americans are angry about immigrationIt's time to face this difficult fact, understand why it's happening, and deal with it. https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/americans-are-angry-about-immigration https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/americans-are-angry-about-immigrationNoah Smith Mon, 27 Nov 2023 09:27:26 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14c76fc6-67ea-472e-8aac-3f3bc750dc99_1600x1185.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14c76fc6-67ea-472e-8aac-3f3bc750dc99_1600x1185.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14c76fc6-67ea-472e-8aac-3f3bc750dc99_1600x1185.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14c76fc6-67ea-472e-8aac-3f3bc750dc99_1600x1185.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14c76fc6-67ea-472e-8aac-3f3bc750dc99_1600x1185.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14c76fc6-67ea-472e-8aac-3f3bc750dc99_1600x1185.jpeg" width="1456" height="1078" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/14c76fc6-67ea-472e-8aac-3f3bc750dc99_1600x1185.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1078,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:458583,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14c76fc6-67ea-472e-8aac-3f3bc750dc99_1600x1185.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14c76fc6-67ea-472e-8aac-3f3bc750dc99_1600x1185.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14c76fc6-67ea-472e-8aac-3f3bc750dc99_1600x1185.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F14c76fc6-67ea-472e-8aac-3f3bc750dc99_1600x1185.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></figure></div><p>上图是<a href="https://smarthistory.org/seeing-america-2/nativism-and-the-know-nothing-party/">一无所知党</a>的支持者于 1850 年左右发布的漫画，该党是一个短命的美国政党，成立于 1800 年代中期，旨在反对移民。 （这个名字应该表明该党是一个秘密社团，而不是其成员是一群无知的傻瓜，尽管在后一点上你可以得出任何你喜欢的结论。）一无所知代表了美国周期性的反社会运动之一。 - 移民的强烈抵制——其他包括 1910 年代本土主义者的强烈抵制，导致了<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Immigration_Act_of_1924">1924 年限制性的约翰逊-里德法案</a>，以及 1990 年代的强烈抵制，导致了<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Personal_Responsibility_and_Work_Opportunity_Act#Provisions">1996 年一项法律</a>，使许多移民没有资格获得福利，以及十年后的<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Secure_Fence_Act_of_2006">《安全围栏法案》</a>之后。</p><p>如果您认为美国始终是一个开放、有吸引力、对移民友好的地方，请再想一想。<em>通常</em>是这样；迄今为止的所有强烈反对最终都消退了，宽松的移民制度又回来了。我们的领导人，从乔治·华盛顿和托马斯·杰斐逊到林登·约翰逊和罗纳德·里根，几乎总是<a href="https://fordmurraylaw.com/presidential-thoughts-on-immigration/">一群支持移民的人</a>。移民在我们国家的自我概念中<a href="https://www.amazon.com/Americanism-Twenty-First-Century-Opinion-Immigration/dp/0521145244">根深蒂固</a>。但每隔一段时间，足够多的美国人就会意识到移民对我们国家构成威胁，他们会采取行动限制这种威胁。</p><p>不幸的是，现在似乎正是这样的时期之一。反移民情绪在特朗普执政期间崩溃，但在拜登领导下卷土重来： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F044fd959-7356-4cd7-b735-deb33ede8971_917x539.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F044fd959-7356-4cd7-b735-deb33ede8971_917x539.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F044fd959-7356-4cd7-b735-deb33ede8971_917x539.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F044fd959-7356-4cd7-b735-deb33ede8971_917x539.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F044fd959-7356-4cd7-b735-deb33ede8971_917x539.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressi